verbose_text: Finally, we identified a characteristic asymmetric line of BRACHYURY expression defining the APE stage of pig and bovine embryos at E12.5 and E17.0, respectively (XREF_FIG B), while OCT4, NANOG, SOX2 and NODAL were still well expressed in the epiblast (XREF_FIG A; Fig. S1A-C).
